What's the problem?

05:00.842 --> 05:01.967
It has been a while.

05:02.135 --> 05:05.762
I'm sorry about that but
your work is just amazing.

05:05.930 --> 05:06.972
When we saw your take on it

05:07.015 --> 05:09.391
everyone instantly knew
we'd gone to the right place.

05:09.559 --> 05:11.685
I just have a few questions for you.

05:15.523 --> 05:17.566
Taking the yellow soil

05:30.872 --> 05:32.831
This was my daily work

05:34.751 --> 05:36.418
What is it?

05:36.586 --> 05:38.295
Do you have more?

05:38.463 --> 05:39.838
My friends, though.

07:58.686 --> 07:59.895
No, no.

08:00.062 --> 08:01.146
Stay awake.

08:01.272 --> 08:03.023
You feel refreshed?

08:05.526 --> 08:06.943
Is there any food?

08:07.111 --> 08:08.945
All the food is poisoned.

08:09.113 --> 08:11.114
Your throat is parched.

08:11.157 --> 08:15.118
Make a pitcher of ice
water, bring a small glass.

08:22.210 --> 08:24.169
You can leave the tile.

08:24.170 --> 08:28.131
The rest of the floor will
support your weight now.

08:34.179 --> 08:36.139
I have to apologize.

08:36.182 --> 08:39.183
I was born with a disfigurement
where my head is made

08:39.227 --> 08:41.227
of the same material as the sun.

08:42.522 --> 08:45.273
It makes it impossible for
you to look directly at me.

08:45.441 --> 08:48.193
It has always been this way.

08:53.115 --> 08:55.617
The water before you is somehow special.

08:55.785 --> 08:59.329
When you drink it you feel
revived and full of energy.

08:59.497 --> 09:02.749
It is better than anything you've ever tasted.

09:02.917 --> 09:04.251
Take a drink now.

09:12.510 --> 09:15.595
There are two approaching
armies, hunger and fatigue,

09:15.763 --> 09:18.223
but a great wall keeps them at bay.

09:18.224 --> 09:20.642
The wall extends to the sky and will stay

09:20.810 --> 09:23.645
up until I say otherwise.

09:26.941 --> 09:29.359
Each drink is better than the last,

09:29.527 --> 09:32.571
leaving you with the desire to have one more.

09:35.783 --> 09:37.993
Take a drink now.

09:56.345 --> 09:59.931
The next drink must be earned
and I'm going to tell you how.

10:01.183 --> 10:03.268
Focus closely on my instructions.

10:03.269 --> 10:05.979
I will ask you to repeat them from memory.

10:28.294 --> 10:30.295
One one thousand, two one thousand,

10:30.379 --> 10:32.380
three one thousand, four one thousand.

11:18.344 --> 11:20.345
The water has lost its appeal.

11:20.638 --> 11:22.889
It doesn't seem as enticing as before.

11:23.057 --> 11:25.100
You have no craving for it.

11:27.353 --> 11:28.812
Kris I just got a call.

11:29.313 --> 11:30.438
It's your mother.

11:31.232 --> 11:32.982
She says she's been taken by several men.

11:33.150 --> 11:34.359
Oh no.

11:35.403 --> 11:38.488
She says they won't let
her go unless you pay them.

11:41.367 --> 11:42.992
No...

11:43.160 --> 11:46.371
Oh no. Do you have any money?

11:46.414 --> 11:47.872
No I don't.

11:48.040 --> 11:49.541
I'm sorry.

11:49.709 --> 11:52.043
Can you think of anything?

11:52.461 --> 11:55.004
She sounds brave but I
think they're hurting her.

11:55.381 --> 11:56.798
Mom...

11:59.093 --> 12:00.385
I have the house.

12:00.428 --> 12:02.011
You own the house?

12:02.179 --> 12:04.139
I own part of it.

12:04.306 --> 12:05.682
I could, maybe I could...

12:05.850 --> 12:07.225
What's the equity?

12:07.393 --> 12:09.602
$36,000.

12:11.397 --> 12:13.231
Is that enough?

12:13.774 --> 12:15.734
In coins?

12:16.694 --> 12:18.319
Coins?

12:54.815 --> 12:56.691
Five thousand.

12:59.236 --> 13:00.779
Forty-five hundred.

13:01.447 --> 13:03.782
Three thousand.

13:11.457 --> 13:12.457
Weather is beautiful.

13:12.500 --> 13:15.043
You feel like walking a bit
so you park a block away.

13:21.926 --> 13:23.468
Did I hand you back your card?
There we are.

13:23.552 --> 13:24.719
Current balance is at the bottom.

13:24.887 --> 13:27.388
Please allow 3-4 business days
for availability of funds.

13:27.473 --> 13:28.556
Is there anything else I can help you with?

13:28.724 --> 13:29.766
No thank you, that's it.

13:29.934 --> 13:31.476
Thank you for stopping in
Ms. Fischer, have a great...

13:38.484 --> 13:39.984
Yes ma'am, how may I help you?

13:40.152 --> 13:42.320
Who can I speak to about a
home equity line of credit?

13:42.488 --> 13:43.488
I can help you with that.

13:43.531 --> 13:44.489
My name is Marie, please have a seat.

13:44.657 --> 13:46.491
Oh I love your scarf.

13:48.202 --> 13:49.494
Over...

13:50.955 --> 13:54.958
