29:02.741 --> 29:04.408
Yeah, that's my handwriting.

29:04.409 --> 29:07.119
This is different obviously.

30:54.894 --> 30:57.271
So we do all their
printing and their literature.

30:57.438 --> 30:59.481
It's just a small school district but,

30:59.524 --> 31:01.525
this is the address right here,

31:01.693 --> 31:04.361
so if you ever need any printing, signage,

31:04.529 --> 31:05.529
just come in or call.

31:05.655 --> 31:06.947
I don't need... I never in a
million years would I ever...

31:07.115 --> 31:08.323
I don't need any signage.

31:08.491 --> 31:09.491
This is you, Kris?

31:09.534 --> 31:10.158
Yeah, that's me.

31:10.326 --> 31:11.034
Okay.

31:11.411 --> 31:12.494
Umm...

31:12.537 --> 31:14.246
I'll call.

31:14.414 --> 31:16.540
I'm not going to call for signage though, right?

31:16.583 --> 31:18.667
I don't need any signage.

31:19.627 --> 31:21.044
Okay, Kris?

31:21.212 --> 31:22.754
Okay, Jeff.

31:25.675 --> 31:27.426
Uh, hey...

31:28.845 --> 31:30.679
