32:41.751 --> 32:43.585
That's what the, that's what the firm does.

32:43.628 --> 32:46.964
It has a commercial half, the
other side's personal wealth.

32:47.131 --> 32:47.756
Where is it?

32:47.924 --> 32:50.592
It's, you can actually see it.

32:50.635 --> 32:51.635
It's a high rise.

32:51.719 --> 32:54.638
The Palomar Building, C&L Crowne, that's us.

32:54.764 --> 32:56.723
Why do you take the train?

32:56.891 --> 32:57.849
