33:03.189 --> 33:04.648
Do you want to see my driver's license?

33:04.691 --> 33:05.649
No.

33:06.651 --> 33:09.653
That's a gift for us.

33:10.321 --> 33:13.281
See there's this path forward
where I wait to tell you

33:13.449 --> 33:15.659
and you either use it as an excuse

33:15.702 --> 33:18.578
or maybe you don't but, I don't know.

33:18.663 --> 33:21.665
I was diagnosed about a
year ago and I take these

33:21.833 --> 33:24.376
and I take those and it's fine.

33:24.544 --> 33:25.961
It seems fine.

33:26.129 --> 33:27.379
It seems fine to me.

33:27.547 --> 33:28.672
So there's that, and...

33:28.715 --> 33:31.425
I think I saved us both three to four weeks.

33:31.592 --> 33:32.551
Alright.

33:33.052 --> 33:34.094
Thank you.

33:34.679 --> 33:36.680
I'm going to get the check and we can...

33:37.640 --> 33:40.559
...get out of here.

33:41.686 --> 33:42.686
I'm sorry.

33:43.688 --> 33:44.813
That was stupid.

33:45.690 --> 33:47.858
I don't know what I'm meant to say to that.

33:48.026 --> 33:49.109
What do I say to that?

33:49.277 --> 33:50.318
I don't know.

33:55.700 --> 33:59.244
Why don't I-I'll tell
you something and then you,

33:59.412 --> 34:02.122
