34:18.723 --> 34:19.723
That's not good right?

34:19.849 --> 34:20.724
It's not great.

34:20.891 --> 34:21.933
Yeah.

34:53.674 --> 34:55.967
Where's Michel?

34:56.135 --> 34:58.345
We have clients with ten times this revenue

34:58.513 --> 34:59.971
