42:10.736 --> 42:13.446
I made a list of the things
I want to try harder at.

42:16.116 --> 42:17.200
I love you.

42:17.743 --> 42:20.286
Those are just words,
they don't fix anything Jill.

42:28.712 --> 42:30.630
