that owns a few of them.

49:37.349 --> 49:39.976
So it's sort of... a perk.

49:40.143 --> 49:41.435
Right, but why do you choose...

49:41.603 --> 49:42.812
I am starving...
Are you hungry?

49:42.980 --> 49:44.522
You've got to be right?

49:47.651 --> 49:49.944
It always just reminds me of family vacations.

49:51.029 --> 49:53.447
Maybe because of the smell of chlorine

49:53.615 --> 49:54.949
and bleach in the sheets,

49:55.117 --> 49:57.785
the glasses wrapped in plastic.

49:59.454 --> 50:00.496
Yeah...

50:00.664 --> 50:02.832
We would go to this...
there's this place in Vermont

50:03.000 --> 50:04.667
that we would go when we were kids.

50:04.668 --> 50:05.960
It's like a colonial...

50:06.128 --> 50:07.503
In Vermont?

50:07.671 --> 50:08.462
Yeah.

50:08.630 --> 50:11.590
It was historic and there was museums,

50:11.675 --> 50:13.676
but the thing that stood out for
us was that they...

50:13.719 --> 50:16.470
we would stay at this hotel with an indoor pool,

50:16.638 --> 50:20.641
and it was just the biggest
deal in the world for us.

50:20.684 --> 50:22.685
Because one, it's indoor...

50:23.687 --> 50:26.647
Two, you can swim... What's
going on with you?

50:30.485 --> 50:32.236
What are you thinking?

50:34.865 --> 50:35.698
Is it good?

50:35.866 --> 50:37.450
No.

51:20.118 --> 51:22.369
You have a message.

51:23.997 --> 51:25.706
Are you going?

51:26.541 --> 51:28.000
To the banquet?

51:30.253 --> 51:32.171
I mean it's going to be work, you know.

51:32.339 --> 51:33.923
It's people from work.

51:34.091 --> 51:35.591
For three hours.

51:40.555 --> 51:42.098
I thought we could go...

51:42.474 --> 51:43.682
...if you want.

51:47.771 --> 51:49.480
You want to?

51:57.447 --> 51:59.447
I'm sorry.

52:13.797 --> 52:15.631
I like you so much.

52:15.799 --> 52:18.676
I do. I like you so much.

52:19.803 --> 52:20.219
I have...

52:20.387 --> 52:21.804
You are kidding right?

52:21.847 --> 52:25.891
I have been really careful
not to lie about something.

52:26.810 --> 52:28.811
And through omission,

52:29.521 --> 52:30.813
I may have given you an impression

52:30.981 --> 52:33.816
that isn't quite real.

52:33.859 --> 52:35.526
I work here.

52:35.694 --> 52:38.737
I work on 29th C&L Crowne.

52:38.864 --> 52:40.447
I'm not an advisor.

52:40.615 --> 52:41.824
I don't broker.

52:42.409 --> 52:46.036
I do interdepartmental reports,
okay, I don't have an office.

52:46.204 --> 52:48.247
I work in common space, I work with interns.

52:48.790 --> 52:50.833
Greg pays me in cash to keep me off their books

52:50.834 --> 52:55.838
