53:12.147 --> 53:14.106
So I am lucky to have this job.

53:16.818 --> 53:18.152
When you walk into that hotel...

53:18.612 --> 53:19.820
you're going to know.

53:19.863 --> 53:21.864
When you walk into that
banquet, you're going to know.

53:21.948 --> 53:23.824
Because everybody there knows.

53:23.867 --> 53:25.242
And they look at me in a certain way,

53:25.410 --> 53:27.077
and they talk to me in a certain way.

53:27.245 --> 53:29.496
In a way that you don't look at me yet.

53:32.626 --> 53:33.626
That was smart.

53:36.963 --> 53:39.506
To wait to tell me.

53:43.678 --> 53:44.845
I'm sorry.

53:49.976 --> 53:51.852
Think you might be using that wrong.

53:53.647 --> 53:56.315
Which direction is this?
Is that east?

53:57.567 --> 53:59.818
You can see the whole city from up here.

54:22.842 --> 54:24.927
